    public class LutColorFilter
extends ImageFilter
implements ImageFilter.FilterConfigIntensity
    Represents a "Look up table" (Lut) ImageFilter For Camera live Preview the filter is OpenGl Based but has also a Renderscript implementation to renderIfNeeded final images in full resolution.
